{"tid":295692,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲都試過病到咁","createTime":"2017-06-24T03:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T22:47:06.000Z","uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97e587e488ddea7b33b20b52450391dcf5191fa5","tid":295692,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"(其實我唔知開係咩台先至開係創意台，希望會有認真嘅建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n話說早兩日返返下part time冇啦啦發燒，仲要係愈燒愈勁個種，返到屋企太辛苦瞓就啦啦聲瞓(~7點)<br />\n明明好攰但係11點就醒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (個時~38.8&deg;C)<br />\n之後點瞓都瞓唔好<br />\n琴日睇咗醫生之後好啲，但係喉嚨開始刺痛，同樣地都係瞓得唔好<br />\n今日起身就喉嚨劇痛，就算啪咗幾粒醫生畀嘅喉糖都冇用，然後又冇胃口食嘢，只係可以飲水<br />\n同埋發現自己手同腳出咗少少紅疹，頭皮出黃色結晶(平時有少少頭皮不過都係白色嘅)， 口入面都生咗幾粒痱滋。<br />\n由於我平時好少病所以我唔知依啲係咪正常反應，同埋間唔中都會再有少少發熱<br />\n喺到唔該晒咁多位巴絲先(如果有錯字請見諒，病到1999咁)"},{"pid":"e20f9ce8232424b55800dc91cb11f66e32f23d38","tid":295692,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:41:56.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304aabbb03603e3e9ce928e83654df0c2f337fd5","tid":295692,"uid":5858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:43:30.000Z","msg":"手足口病 好似係<br />\n<br />\nbtw 睇多次醫生 如果真係中招嘅會俾1個禮拜假紙你"},{"pid":"926d6cdf34dc46fed85a469e0090b0976977bf0e","tid":295692,"uid":5858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:44:36.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦 仲上網問人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff00a8759ce6ee6f9edfd8f844aae47f4cc05d76","tid":295692,"uid":1589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:45:07.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"827fc5ed4b8f3fea85a2817814e2fca6432dac33","tid":295692,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:45:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>手足口病 好似係<br />\n<br />\nbtw 睇多次醫生 如果真係中招嘅會俾1個禮拜假紙你</blockquote><br />\n唔係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50eb9c8e2a82bb2556bef350c5cd15244b49b5b","tid":295692,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:45:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇醫生啦 仲上網問人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇咗冇咩用先上嚟問"},{"pid":"b058e9c0115f5d8b04a642bc1f12a3ec14d2f292","tid":295692,"uid":78777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:54:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>手足口病 好似係<br />\n<br />\nbtw 睇多次醫生 如果真係中招嘅會俾1個禮拜假紙你</blockquote><br />\n啱啱上網睇過又有啲唔同，我個啲疹係似敏感一粒粒好少個種，同埋冇係手腳掌出現，係得手臂同大脾先有。 BTW 唔該晒巴打先"},{"pid":"2610f5421a12356e009a4df586c5074883273c00","tid":295692,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:02:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇醫生啦 仲上網問人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇咗冇咩用先上嚟問</blockquote><br />\n所以你覺得連登有醫生？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw手足口病"},{"pid":"33f05843bbd7226e6485ec30ca386956f472cd40","tid":295692,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:37:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇醫生啦 仲上網問人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇咗冇咩用先上嚟問</blockquote><br />\n所以你覺得連登有醫生？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw手足口病</blockquote><br />\n等緊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望真係唔會中手足口病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e22002108de7fee22a83e3df71c4dd4f8bc4482","tid":295692,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"巴打我點睇你都係手足口病<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申中過招<br />\n建議你買定幾筒得果定"},{"pid":"44df659d3cf0bd7d3044fb305e60c24222cc9297","tid":295692,"uid":19404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"試過 入左院七日不藥而癒<br />\n好似係免疫系統自己打自己"},{"pid":"39b3b90fd6d731cef02b7d8710407f17ad358ee9","tid":295692,"uid":47936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"手足口"},{"pid":"ded48a1134981059cdabd234412ed03620ef9c63","tid":295692,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:43:49.000Z","msg":"玩撚完手足口病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a062bffeefc79edc3a3cf8ea03e511465589884d","tid":295692,"uid":86762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:45:19.000Z","msg":"以前自己一個喺海外住果陣都試過<br />\n係好辛苦 水就要喪飲㗎啦<br />\n飲到差唔多每 十零廿分鐘去一次廁所<br />\n嘢食就食番清淡啲 最好煲粥<br />\n食返啲退燒藥 有足夠休息<br />\n最快三日好返 正常都要四五六日<br />\n我嗰陣冇睇醫生 如果過咗成個禮拜都係咁 再睇醫生啦<br />\n祝早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a516572f3172066232de806816526787e3805af","tid":295692,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:45:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打我點睇你都係手足口病<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申中過招<br />\n建議你買定幾筒得果定</blockquote><br />\n使立消好食啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw係咪真係會口腔潰瘍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7059818f8a4df5d90309ca0affae7f99af65fc","tid":295692,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:46:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩撚完手足口病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇掂過小朋友，成日都有洗手咁都會中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪啲客傳畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805715340bade591533f60102ca1ee7df125ab02","tid":295692,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前自己一個喺海外住果陣都試過<br />\n係好辛苦 水就要喪飲㗎啦<br />\n飲到差唔多每 十零廿分鐘去一次廁所<br />\n嘢食就食番清淡啲 最好煲粥<br />\n食返啲退燒藥 有足夠休息<br />\n最快三日好返 正常都要四五六日<br />\n我嗰陣冇睇醫生 如果過咗成個禮拜都係咁 再睇醫生啦<br />\n祝早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食粥有啲咩料可以落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 琴日食咗兩淡白粥有啲反胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw 多謝巴打，祝你身體健康，唔好再病啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0ad30afa1c54e6d043de12b033d3eb24c6b7f0","tid":295692,"uid":19858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:55:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>玩撚完手足口病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇掂過小朋友，成日都有洗手咁都會中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪啲客傳畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔一定接觸小朋友<br />\n可能接觸到帶菌病人<br />\n我份工都無小朋友，不過經我女友惹到<br />\n探一探佢就中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n病癥都係喉嚨劇痛，會見到喉嚨生白點類似痱滋<br />\n果種痛同以前喉嚨痛完全唔同lv<br />\n食份三文治食左半個鐘，飲水都劇痛<br />\n發燒、手腳出紅點，慢慢會好痕<br />\n但其實睇醫生食藥都好快好<br />\n後期喉嚨無咁痛都幾爽<br />\n因為退左燒你同正常人無分別<br />\n唔似傷風感冒咁辛苦<br />\n但醫生又焗住寫七日假俾你因爲高傳染性<br />\n安心喺屋企食同訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5138143709c4199960c5983166e75eee369c52b","tid":295692,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T05:01:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>玩撚完手足口病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇掂過小朋友，成日都有洗手咁都會中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪啲客傳畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔一定接觸小朋友<br />\n可能接觸到帶菌病人<br />\n我份工都無小朋友，不過經我女友惹到<br />\n探一探佢就中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n病癥都係喉嚨劇痛，會見到喉嚨生白點類似痱滋<br />\n果種痛同以前喉嚨痛完全唔同lv<br />\n食份三文治食左半個鐘，飲水都劇痛<br />\n發燒、手腳出紅點，慢慢會好痕<br />\n但其實睇醫生食藥都好快好<br />\n後期喉嚨無咁痛都幾爽<br />\n因為退左燒你同正常人無分別<br />\n唔似傷風感冒咁辛苦<br />\n但醫生又焗住寫七日假俾你因爲高傳染性<br />\n安心喺屋企食同訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱啱睇完醫生確定係中咗招<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要同你講啲症狀一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個醫生話唔使戒口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd58634b171f5c150d6b726b7e8f51999fffa27","tid":295692,"uid":5858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T06:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>玩撚完手足口病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇掂過小朋友，成日都有洗手咁都會中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪啲客傳畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔一定接觸小朋友<br />\n可能接觸到帶菌病人<br />\n我份工都無小朋友，不過經我女友惹到<br />\n探一探佢就中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n病癥都係喉嚨劇痛，會見到喉嚨生白點類似痱滋<br />\n果種痛同以前喉嚨痛完全唔同lv<br />\n食份三文治食左半個鐘，飲水都劇痛<br />\n發燒、手腳出紅點，慢慢會好痕<br />\n但其實睇醫生食藥都好快好<br />\n後期喉嚨無咁痛都幾爽<br />\n因為退左燒你同正常人無分別<br />\n唔似傷風感冒咁辛苦<br />\n但醫生又焗住寫七日假俾你因爲高傳染性<br />\n安心喺屋企食同訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱啱睇完醫生確定係中咗招<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要同你講啲症狀一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個醫生話唔使戒口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係就係唔洗戒口 過幾日爛口就真係痛到仆街<br />\n<br />\n困自己喺房 儘量唔好同人接觸 好易野到人"},{"pid":"a554210388039097c6561173bc8e28140643dc1f","tid":295692,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>玩撚完手足口病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇掂過小朋友，成日都有洗手咁都會中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪啲客傳畀我<img src=